3. cs.LG - The paper uses deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and falls under the category of learning.
4. cs.RO - The paper deals with the optimization of traffic flow, which can be categorized under robotics and automation.
5. cs.CE - The paper deals with the control of traffic signals, which can be categorized under control engineering.
